abstract: >-
  A documentation-integrated Lean 4 publication artifact for a finite,
  target-preserving rooted-tree leaf-summation mechanism in polymer cluster
  expansions with holes. The artifact exposes three stable theorem endpoints
  and pins the exact upstream proof source, Lean toolchain, and Mathlib revision.
